PATTERNS "ADVENTURE CRAFTS" "CRAFTING PATTERNS" SCHEMATICS DESIGNS

Some items can be found in adventures which teach you new crafting recipes.
These are usually called 'patterns', 'designs', 'schematics', or 'recipes'.
Crafts from patterns are not limited by the levels of your skills or the
ability used to make them.

The level of the crafted item is based on your crafting level, but many
patterns have their own upper limit. Usually the pattern will mention if
there's a limit.
  
You can see the level range of the item a pattern makes on its info display.

