"VERDANT LEATHERS" "BRIAR HIDE" "ABSINTHIAN LEATHER"

Verdant Leathers (Trade ability)
Command:  craft <briar hide | absinthian leather>

Certain tradesmen learn to treat fine leather with a bath of herbs, creating
magical leathers that are used to make the finest leather weapons and armor.

These leathers are generally used in crafts in the 200-300 level range.

